 calle de la Amargura'' || data-sort-value=\"Ripstein\"| [[Arturo Ripstein]] || Mexico Spain\n|-\n| ''[[Don't Be Bad]]'' || ''Non essere cattivo'' || data-sort-value=\"Caligari\"| [[Claudio Caligari]] || Italy\n|-\n| colspan=2| ''[[Everest (2015 film)|Everest]]'' || data-sort-value=\"Kormakur\"| [[Baltasar Korm\u00e1kur]] || United States\n|-\n| colspan=2| ''[[Go with Me (film)|Go With Me]]'' || data-sort-value=\"Alfredson\"| [[Daniel Alfredson]] || United States, Canada, Sweden\n|-\n| ''[[Mr. Six (film)|Mr. Six]]'' || ''Lao Pao Er'' ( \u8001\u70ae\u513f ) || data-sort-value=\"Hu\"| [[Guan Hu]] || China\n|-\n| colspan=2| ''[[Spotlight (film)|Spotlight]]'' || data-sort-value=\"McCarthy\"| [[Tom McCarthy (director)|Tom McCarthy]] || United States\n|}\n{| class=\"sortable wikitable\" style=\"width:95%; margin-top:2px\"\n! colspan=4| Documentaries\n|-\n! English title\n! Original title\n! Director(s)\n! Production country\n|-\n| colspan=2| ''[[De Palma (film)|De Palma]]'' || data-sort-value=\"Baumbach\"| [[Noah Baumbach]], [[Jake Paltrow]] || United States\n|-\n| style=\"background: #ececec; font-size: smaller; text-align: center\" data-sort-value=\"Esercito\"| N/A || data-sort-value=\"Esercito\"| ''L'esercito piu piccolo del mondo'' || data-sort-value=\"Pannone\"| [[Gianfranco Pannone]] || Vatican City State\n|-\n| data-sort-value=\"Event\"| ''[[The Event (2015 film)|The Event]]'' || ''Sobytie'' || data-sort-value=\"Loznitsa\"| [[Sergei Loznitsa]] || Netherlands, Belgium\n|-\n| colspan=2| ''[[Human (2015 film)|Human]]'' (special screening)<ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.labiennale.org/en/cinema/72nd-festival/screenings/12sept.html |title=70th Venice Film Festival - Sceening schedule 12 September |work=labiennale.org |url-status=dead |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20150913184016/http://www.labiennale.org/en/cinema/72nd-festival/screenings/12sept.html |archivedate=13 September 2015  |access-date=4 May 2018 }}</ref> || data-sort-value=\"Arthus\"| [[Yann Arthus-Bertrand]] || France\n|-\n| colspan=2| ''[[In Jackson Heights]]'' || data-sort-value=\"Wiseman\"| [[Frederick Wiseman]] || United States\n|-\n| colspan=2| ''[[Janis: Little Girl Blue|Janis]]'' || data-sort-value=\"Berg\"| [[Amy J. Berg]] || United States\n|-\n| style=\"background: #ececec; font-size: smaller; text-align: center\" data-sort-value=\"Ricordi\"| N/A || ''I ricordi del fiume'' || data-sort-value=\"Maresco\"| [[Cipr\u00ec & Maresco|Franco Maresco]] || Italy\n|-\n| style=\"background: #ececec; font-size: smaller; text-align: center\" data-sort-value=\"Uomini\"| N/A || ''Gli uomini di questa citt\u00e0 io non li conosco'' || data-sort-value=\"Maresco\"| [[Cipr\u00ec & Maresco|Franco Maresco]] || Italy\n|-\n| ''[[Winter on Fire: Ukraine's Fight for Freedom|Winter on Fire]]''  || ''Zyma y vohni'' (\u0417\u0438\u043c\u0430 \u0443 \u0432\u043e\u0433\u043d\u0456) || data-sort-value=\"Afineevsky\"| [[Evgeny Afineevsky]] || Ukraine\n|}\n\n===Horizons===\nThe following feature films were selected for the ''Horizons (Orizzonti)'' section:<ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.labiennale.org/en/cinema/72nd-festival/line-up/off-sel/orizzonti/ |title=Orizzonti |work=labiennale.org |url-status=dead |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20151001042006/http://www.labiennale.org/en/cinema/72nd-festival/line-up/off-sel/orizzonti/ |archivedate=1 October 2015  |access-date=14 April 2018 }}</ref><ref name=\"InComp\" /><ref name=\"Variety\"/>\n\n{| class=\"sortable wikitable\" style=\"width:95%; margin-bottom:0px\"\n! colspan=4| Feature films\n|-\n! English title\n! Original title\n! Director(s)\n! Production country\n|-\n| ''[[Burning Love (film)|Burning Love]]'' || ''Pecore In Erba'' || data-sort-value=\"Caviglia\"| [[Alberto Caviglia]] || Italy\n|-\n| colspan=2 data-sort-value=\"Childhood\"| ''[[The Childhood of a Leader (film)|The Childhood of a Leader]]'' || data-sort-value=\"Corbet\"| [[Brady Corbet]] || United Kingdom, Hungary, Belgium, France\n|-\n| colspan=2 data-sort-value=\