017/http://www.labiennale.org/en/cinema/72nd-festival/line-up/off-sel/out-of-competition/ |archivedate=1 October 2015  |access-date=14 April 2018 }}</ref><ref name=\"InComp\" /><ref name=\"Variety\" />\n\n{| class=\"sortable wikitable\" style=\"width:95%; margin-bottom:0px\"\n! colspan=4| Fiction films\n|-\n! English title\n! Original title\n! Director(s)\n! Production country\n|-\n| ''Afternoon'' || ''Na ri xia wu'' ( \u90a3\u65e5\u4e0b\u5348 ) || data-sort-value=\"Ming\"| [[Tsai Ming-liang]] || Taiwan\n|-\n| colspan=2| ''[[Black Mass (film)|Black Mass]]'' || data-sort-value=\"Cooper\"| [[Scott Cooper (director)|Scott Cooper]] || United States\n|-\n| ''[[Bleak Street]]'' || data-sort-value=\"Calle\"| ''La calle de la Amargura'' || data-sort-value=\"Ripstein\"| [[Arturo Ripstein]] || Mexico Spain\n|-\n| ''[[Don't Be Bad]]'' || ''Non essere cattivo'' || data-sort-value=\"Caligari\"| [[Claudio Caligari]] || Italy\n|-\n| colspan=2| ''[[Everest (2015 film)|Everest]]'' || data-sort-value=\"Kormakur\"| [[Baltasar Korm\u00e1kur]] || United States\n|-\n| colspan=2| ''[[Go with Me (film)|Go With Me]]'' || data-sort-value=\"Alfredson\"| [[Daniel Alfredson]] || United States, Canada, Sweden\n|-\n| ''[[Mr. Six (film)|Mr. Six]]'' || ''Lao Pao Er'' ( \u8001\u70ae\u513f ) || data-sort-value=\"Hu\"| [[Guan Hu]] || China\n|-\n| colspan=2| ''[[Spotlight (film)|Spotlight]]'' || data-sort-value=\"McCarthy\"| [[Tom McCarthy (director)|Tom McCarthy]] || United States\n|}\n{| class=\"sortable wikitable\" style=\"width:95%; margin-top:2px\"\n! colspan=4| Documentaries\n|-\n! English title\n! Original title\n! Director(s)\n! Production country\n|-\n| colspan=2| ''[[De Palma (film)|De Palma]]'' || data-sort-value=\"Baumbach\"| [[Noah Baumbach]], [[Jake Paltrow]] || United States\n|-\n| style=\"background: #ececec; font-size: smaller; text-align: center\" data-sort-value=\"Esercito\"| N/A || data-sort-value=\"Esercito\"| ''L'esercito piu piccolo del mondo'' || data-sort-value=\"Pannone\"| [[G